text: Chorrera may refer to: * Chorrera culture, pre-Columbian civilisation of Ecuador and southern Colombia * Chorrera Formation, Pliocene geologic formation of the Altiplano Cundiboyacense, Colombia * Chorrera (moth), a genus of snout moths * Torreón de la Chorrera, fortified tower in Havana, Cuba * Chorreras, Spain, a site in southeastern Spain formerly host to a Phoenician colony
title: Chorrera (disambiguation)
